commit_list.message:
Add JetBrains comment

Hi  Kacper,
Thank you for the nice write up on TeamCity security.
Would it be possible to add a comment from us? I represent TeamCity team and you can check I belong to JetBrains organization on GitHub.
If you find it appropriate to add the comment in some other way, please let me know.
Fix support for multiple VCS roots?
